name: Bird Gang
description:
Color: Turquoise
Fabric: Cotton

Description: The leader of the gang in a red cap says that even bird flu won’t move them. Currently sitting on the turquoise.

- 100% high quality cotton
- Weight of 150g/m2
- Lasting print on front and back of the t-shirt
- Printed tag on the back of the neck instead of scratching tags
- Double stitched neck welt
- Fabric is certified Oeko-Tex Standard 100, Report No. 48118/IIMW that meets all the requirements related to the protection of the environment, while ensuring safety and comfort of use.
